The sources are located at SourceForge.net Mercurial repository.

MJIN:
    http://osrpgcreation.hg.sourceforge.net:8000/hgroot/osrpgcreation/mjin
MJ:
    http://osrpgcreation.hg.sourceforge.net:8000/hgroot/osrpgcreation/mj

You can get them with the following command:
    hg clone URL [DIR]

To build it, read the following Wiki pages:
    1. http://code.google.com/p/ogstudio/wiki/InstallMJIN
    2. http://code.google.com/p/ogstudio/wiki/InstallMJ

